        <div class="body">
            <p>Route parameters (also known as template parameters in HTTP language) are <em>not</em> query parameters. Query paramters are like <a href="http://example.com?name=bar">http://example.com?name=bar</a></p>

<p>What you are looking for is the RouteMatch object:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$this-&gt;getEvent()-&gt;getRouteMatch()-&gt;getParam('name');
</code></pre>

